Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你到底要去哪里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看来你们已经接手了地面的工作\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, you seem to have taken over the effort aboveground.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我要去处理别的事情了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I have other things to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎对 尤其是有一件事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yeah. One thing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,‎听着 我们在浪费时间\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Look, we're done screwing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你要给我们看传说中的地下宫廷\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You are going to show us your fabled underground court.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后我们要让这里秩序井然\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And then we are going to get this place in proper order,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.31,0:06:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎保卫人民 清理城市\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}defend the people and clean out the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎明白了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are we clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想是时候带你们去地下宫廷了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think it's time for you to go to the Underground Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是啊 我刚刚不是这么说的吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yeah, isn't that what I just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚才唠叨想要什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I stopped listening a second or two
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎后来我就没听你说话了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}after you started mewling about what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后我决定 是时候让你们跟着我了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Then I decided it was time for you to follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎认清你们的处境\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Know your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.68,0:07:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们先看看这个地方 好吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Let's take a look at this place first, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真是杰作\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Masterly, masterly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,‎多么糟糕的涂鸦\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What an awful bloody daub.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没人会留意这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Nobody's going to miss that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我找到位置了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I have the location,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在做准备\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and I am preparing the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎现在该追求准确和卓越\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It is the time for accuracy, excellence,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎还要相信你们这些人的勇气\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and whatever passes for courage in you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,‎嘘\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Boo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你真是好人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}That was nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我没发现还有人在看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I didn't realize anyone was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在找你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎想象一下 我有多惊讶 你从天而降\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Imagine my surprise when you dropped out of the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎把这些小混蛋吓得魂飞魄散\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and frightened a year's growth out of the little bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎抱歉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不 说真的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你是个好人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎根本没有一个大人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They don't all have an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,会关注他们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}who'll pay any attention at all to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.46,0:10:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎更不用说像死神一样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Let alone plummet down on them
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,从天而降出现在他们面前了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}like death from above, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你让他们有了一个永远流传下去的故事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You gave them a story they'll be telling forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我听到他们在笑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I heard them laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这里好久没有孩子们的欢笑了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's been a while since children laughed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你找我有事吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You were looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.68,0:10:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我想跟你谈谈防御的事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I wanted to talk to you about defenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我还想问问你的食物供应\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And I wanted to ask about your food supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不确定有多少食物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I'm not sure there's much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎问题就在这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, that's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我希望我们可以用一些你的肉干\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was hoping we could use some of the dried meat you have
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎把饭菜做得更好一些\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to make meals go a little further?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎都用了吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Use it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真的吗 ‎\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你能找到什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Whatever you can find.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我早上吃新鲜的食物\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I tended to forage fresh food in the mornings,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我肯定储藏室里有一些腌制食品\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}but I'm sure I have some preserved things in the pantries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你不知道你的城堡里有什么吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You don't actually know what you've got in your castle, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不太清楚\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看来你几个月前还能养活\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It looks like you were feeding an army in there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,一支军队\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}up until a couple of months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是啊...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那不是我的本意\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}that wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但我明白你的意思\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But I take your point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我有点心事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've been preoccupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎除了弥补造成的伤害…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Beyond clearing up some of the damage from...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们谈点别的吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Let's talk about something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎防御\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Defenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是说 ‎我希望只要关上城堡大门\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I mean, I hope just closing your castle doors
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就能把人挡在外面 但是…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}will keep people away, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,‎天很快就要黑了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're going to start losing the light soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我带你去看存放武器的地方...\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Let me show you where the weapons are kept...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后再看看外面\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and then we'll look at the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们记得黑人拉杜\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We remember Radu the Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我的天啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,‎在这里等着\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我的天啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Bloody hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:14:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这太可怕了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎对 但我不是那个意思\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yeah, but that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不可能\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你发现新玩具了吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You found a new toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不是玩具\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎到底是什么啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What on earth is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎据传说 ‎有个疯狂的挪威吸血鬼猎人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, the story goes that a mad Norwegian vampire hunter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,去了印度\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}went to India,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他说服了拉贾普特拉部族的‎兵器大师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and he convinced the weapons master of the Raja-Putra clans
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,给他做了这个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to make him this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎世上仅此一件\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There's only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在我母亲的书里看过画像\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I saw drawings of it in my mother's books.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真正的问题是 怎么会在这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The real question is how it ended up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看到了吗 十字架标志\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}See? Sign of the cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这个吸血鬼猎人死在印度了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Did the vampire hunter die in India?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为印度吸血鬼根本不知道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because Hindu vampires wouldn't have the faintest idea
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他为什么挥舞十字架\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}why he was waving a cross at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:16:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那倒不是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Actually, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎吸血鬼基本上是进化的捕食者\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Vampires are basically an evolved predator species,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以他们的视力与我们有很大不同\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}so their eyesight is pretty different to ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果你用巨大的几何形物体\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Turns out that if you put a big geometric shape
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,‎逼近他们的视野\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}right up close in their field of vision,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这会迷惑他们的大脑\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}it confuses the shit out of their brains
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎让他们惊慌失措\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and, you know, makes them panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你怎么知道这个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}How do you even know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎哦 我曾经想成为英勇的怪物猎人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yeah, I learned all kinds of things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.38,0:16:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我为此学到了很多东西 记得吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}when I was going to be a heroic monster hunter, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎后来发生了这些破事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And then all the shit happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我就慢慢地全忘了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and bit by bit I suppose I lost it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.07,0:16:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,‎现在我又开始回忆起来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And now I'm starting to pick it all up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,‎问题是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎如果你把这东西扔在这里\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}if you're keeping stuff like this down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那你为什么不在地面上用呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}then why aren't you using it up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为你的君主希望如此\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because your betters wish it so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那我该见见他们了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Then it's time I meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎从这里进去见他们吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are they through there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我没说你可以见他们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, I didn't say you could meet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们在休息\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They're resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.45,0:16:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吧 是时候从沉睡中醒来了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yeah, well, time to stop sleeping through all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看着我的眼睛\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Look into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.85,0:16:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你现在真的想让我的生活\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you really, really want to make my life
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,更烦心吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}any more annoying right now, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎醒醒 你们这群混蛋\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Wakey wakey, you shower of assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你不能这样对他们说话\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You cannot speak to them like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我明白他们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, I see why
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎为什么对任何事都漠不关心了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}they're so remarkably unconcerned about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎求你小声点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.34,0:17:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎为什么 他们又不会醒来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why? They're not going to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这里的其他人不知道王室的沉睡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The others here don't understand about the royal sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎扎姆菲尔 ‎这两个人需要安息\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Zamfir, these two need to be laid to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这样真的不行\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is just wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你们有神父吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you have a priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.22,0:17:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没有神父\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No priests.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎扎姆菲尔 听我说\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Zamfir, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这都结束了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎永远不会结束\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It will never be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎末日永远不会征服我们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The apocalypse will never claim us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,塔哥维斯特的灾难永远不会再发生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The catastrophe of Targoviste will never happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们杀了所有神父\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We killed all the priests, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真的吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们正在夺回对国家的控制权\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We are taking back control of our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,塔哥维斯特不是国家\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Targoviste isn't a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是这个国家跳动的心脏\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's the beating heart of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.09,0:18:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎连城市都不是\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not even a city.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是世界上最伟大的城市\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's the greatest city in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们是城市的管理者\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We are its stewards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎-我们要夺回控制权 ‎-控制权 是的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- We're taking back control. - Control? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎让你们的人民挨饿\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Letting your people starve
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎从自己的粪便旁边走过\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and swim around in their own shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不帮助组织他们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not helping them organize.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不帮助他们自卫\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Not helping them defend themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我还没给他们擦屁股呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I haven't been wiping their asses either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是不是应该拿着破布赶过去\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Should I nip back up there with some rags?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你可以试着帮他们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You could try giving them the aid
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,过自己的生活\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to live their damn lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们带了这么多人到下面\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We've taken so many people in down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是的 你收留的这些人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes, you've made an interesting collection
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,明显将死于忽视\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}of people who are clearly dying of neglect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.09,0:18:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们在地下宫廷没有忽视任何人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We neglect no one in the Underground Court.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这些人嘴唇干裂\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}These people have cracked lips,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,后面就有流水\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and you have flowing water back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.97,0:18:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们需要水来防御\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We need that. For defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎圣水\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Holy water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你杀了所有神父 从哪弄来的圣水\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Where did you get it if you killed all the priests?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.47,0:19:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们从没有受损的宗教建筑里找到的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We recovered it from intact religious buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你知道有些神父曾经把圣水‎装在木桶\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do you know some of them used to cask and bottle
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,和瓶子里卖吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}holy water to sell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你可以把圣水给人们饮用\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You could have used it to give people something to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们必须保卫宫廷\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The court must be defended.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎要是我们让人们喝光圣水\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What if we'd let people drink it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,‎吸血鬼穿过干涸的地道\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and then vampires crossed empty channels
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎进入宫廷杀死所有人 该怎么办\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to enter the court and kill everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎当然 你不能冒险让吸血鬼进来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Sure. You couldn't risk letting vampires in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们可能已经准备好了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They might have tidied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这根本不管用\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, that doesn't even work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你保护的是两具尸体\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you're defending two dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们会醒来的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They will wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎陛下会从王室沉睡中醒来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Their majesties will awaken from their royal sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎拯救我们所有人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and save us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你疯了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You're insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我当然是疯了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Of course I'm insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎究竟怎么了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The fuck what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎德古拉进城的那天 我就疯了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I went insane the day Dracula hit the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我在天空中看到他的脸\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I saw his face in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,‎就像恶魔本人摧毁了世界\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was like the devil himself punched the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看到地狱触碰你的家园\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}How could you not lose your mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你怎么能不发疯呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}seeing hell touch your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,‎从那以后 我每晚仅睡两个小时\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I sleep for two hours a night and wake up screaming
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后尖叫着醒来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}ever since it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以你还没疯到不知道自己疯了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So you're not so crazy that you don't know you're crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们会醒来的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They will wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是魔法师\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They are magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们有王室血统\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They are royal blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们在隐秘的王国旅行\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They journey in the subtle realms
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎以恢复他们的力量\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}to recover their strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.30,0:20:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,‎在此之前 我必须保护他们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and I have to defend them until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我现在懂了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你已经受苦太久了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You have been suffering for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你是德古拉伯爵来袭时‎最后一个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Were you the last person of noble birth left alive
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,活着的贵族吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}when Dracula struck?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我没有受苦\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am not suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是一项伟大的事业\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is the great work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.07,0:20:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是我光荣的职责\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is my glorious duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎通过拯救他们 我将拯救所有人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I will save everyone by saving them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,‎难怪他们把它打碎了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Well, no wonder they broke it into pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是你把他们从宫殿废墟里拖出来的吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Did you drag them out of the ruins of their palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.12,0:20:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那是我的责任 我救了他们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It was my job. I saved them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们会醒来的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They will wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.87,0:20:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们会拯救我们所有人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They will save us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一切就会回归正常\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And everything will be set right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一切都将恢复原样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Everything will be as it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们是魔法师 赛珐\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They are magicians, Sypha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎是吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:20:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,‎神父阶层总是怀疑这件事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The priest class always suspected it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们骚扰王室 你能相信吗 但你看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They harried the royal family. Can you believe it? But look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.27,0:21:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看看我们从他们的宫殿里‎找到的所有东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Look at all the things we recovered from their palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎看看他们神秘的宝藏\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Behold their mystical treasures.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我救了他们 所以他们会救我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I saved them. So they will save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你在那边浪费时间浪费够了没\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Are you done farting around over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.12,0:21:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我不知道是谁教你这些话的 不过 浪费够了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I don't know who taught you all these words, but yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好 很好\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Okay. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.62,0:21:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,‎对于发生在你身上的一切 ‎我真的很抱歉\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am truly sorry for everything that has happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但现在必须停止这一切\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But all this has to stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,‎什么\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们需要帮助这些人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We need to get these people help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们需要给健康的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We need to arm the healthy ones
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,‎装备你这里的武器\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}with the weapons you have down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们需要放弃这个地方 组织…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We need to abandon this space, organize and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎放弃\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Abandon?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,‎放弃王室吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Abandon the royal family?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是个烂摊子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你尽力了 但你的统治者已经死了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You did the best you could, but your rulers are dead
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎人民需要你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and the people need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不 我救了他们\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No. I saved them.
